{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 408.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "The sun was shining on us in the hot closed-- there was very little oxygen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Extremely hot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I know we all stripped to the waist, took off everything-- shirts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And even then, we had difficulty getting air.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "The older people passed out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And some of them died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "The train was standing there all day, from 9 o'clock in the morning until sunset, in the terrific heat-- no water, nothing, just boiling hot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, around that time, around sunset time, this train-- train started to move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then a bit of air came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we went, the train-- the train went in, right to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was a special railway track-- industrial track, which was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went through the whole-- whole outer suburbs of the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And wherever we went, the Hungarians were jumping around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The children had balloons in their hands.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're shouting that ah, the bloody Jews are going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Wonderful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have no more Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Isn't that a wonderful day?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About five days later, the Russians almost wiped out the whole city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had massive bombing attack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only learned about this in Auschwitz, where we read in the papers it was a huge bombing attacks against this city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] that was-- that was a good-- good news for us, when we arrived to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, but at this stage we were in the wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] you want to know what happened on the trip, or--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the biggest problem was, of course, to-- the toilet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the toilet problem was a very big problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, what happened eventually, that one mans-- two men were in charge of the toilet.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
